<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span class="title"><strong>ON THE AGENDA</strong> <span class="divider"> | </span></span> The <b> S.&#038;P. Case/Shiller Home Price Index for April </b> is out at 9 a.m. The Conference Boardâs <b> Consumer Confidence Index for June </b> is out at 10 a.m. <b> ConAgra Foods</b> is among the companies reporting earnings today. <b> James Bullard,</b> president of the Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis, speaks at the Emerging Leaders Venture Summit in St. Louis at 5 p.m. (6 p.m. E.D.T.). <b> Jerome H. Powell</b>, a Federal Reserve governor, is on CNBC at 8 a.m. and <b> Julian Robertson</b>, founder of Tiger Management, is on at 4:20 p.m.</p>
